1
00:00:17,014 --> 00:00:18,599
Two pieces of the puzzle.

2
00:00:19,016 --> 00:00:20,643
has landed in my lap.

3
00:00:22,061 --> 00:00:23,499
First, you.

4
00:00:23,592 --> 00:00:25,722
Exceptionally rare blood type

5
00:00:25,747 --> 00:00:28,500
with an exceptionally rare blood component.

6
00:00:29,069 --> 00:00:30,112
What happened?

7
00:00:30,652 --> 00:00:32,028
You came back to me.

8
00:00:32,196 --> 00:00:33,572
That’s what happened.

9
00:00:33,614 --> 00:00:35,783
Hand over Ms. Shion to us

10
00:00:35,871 --> 00:00:36,877
and maybe

11
00:00:37,594 --> 00:00:38,970
just maybe

12
00:00:38,995 --> 00:00:40,413
we’ll let you live.

13
00:00:40,580 --> 00:00:41,889
Will you hand her over to us?

14
00:00:41,914 --> 00:00:43,665
or should I justy kill you both?

15
00:00:43,690 --> 00:00:44,639
Brother?

16
00:00:50,699 --> 00:00:52,367
You should have killed me that night.

17
00:01:09,730 --> 00:01:10,957
Do you remember now?

18
00:01:12,016 --> 00:01:13,044
Lux...

19
00:01:14,646 --> 00:01:16,022
It's been a long time

20
00:01:16,442 --> 00:01:17,785
Mr. Francisco...

21
00:01:19,296 --> 00:01:20,403
Madam Violet

22
00:01:21,712 --> 00:01:23,289
Francisco, what's the meaning of this?

23
00:01:23,829 --> 00:01:26,123
You promised me you would kill him!

24
00:01:28,003 --> 00:01:29,009
Lux?

25
00:01:29,847 --> 00:01:30,795
Luxury.

26
00:01:31,999 --> 00:01:33,334
Luxury Valdez...

27
00:01:34,143 --> 00:01:35,185
my older brother.

28
00:01:36,529 --> 00:01:38,239
Raze is your brother?

29
00:01:38,579 --> 00:01:39,637
Are you serious?

30
00:01:40,062 --> 00:01:41,730
Why didn't you tell me?

31
00:01:44,333 --> 00:01:45,584
I couldn't tell you.

32
00:01:46,489 --> 00:01:47,525
I'm sorry.

33
00:01:48,297 --> 00:01:49,412
But from now on

34
00:01:50,292 --> 00:01:51,442
I'll tell you everything.

35
00:01:52,137 --> 00:01:53,179
No more secrets.

36
00:01:54,253 --> 00:01:57,200
You have a lot of explaining to do.

37
00:01:58,378 --> 00:02:00,737
I'll have all the time in
the world after this, darling.

38
00:02:04,353 --> 00:02:05,530
How did you escape?

39
00:02:09,637 --> 00:02:11,181
How did you survive?

40
00:02:12,758 --> 00:02:14,843
I learned it from you.

41
00:02:16,169 --> 00:02:17,815
Not all your friends

42
00:02:18,444 --> 00:02:20,189
are your allies.

43
00:02:21,383 --> 00:02:22,802
What are you insinuating?

44
00:02:26,196 --> 00:02:27,280
Dr. Razon

45
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:30,558
he saved me.

46
00:02:52,630 --> 00:02:55,043
He was the one who helped me pick myself up

47
00:02:55,579 --> 00:02:59,442
so I can avenge the lives you took from us.

48
00:03:01,035 --> 00:03:02,024
Traitor.

49
00:03:02,395 --> 00:03:04,579
I'm surrounded by traitors!

50
00:03:04,604 --> 00:03:05,559
Traitor?

51
00:03:06,983 --> 00:03:08,859
That's not what you call a person

52
00:03:08,901 --> 00:03:10,361
who was never on your side.

53
00:03:10,866 --> 00:03:12,112
Be quiet!

54
00:03:12,488 --> 00:03:14,573
Do you really think we're your underlings?

55
00:03:17,505 --> 00:03:19,257
Everyone's turning on you.

56
00:03:20,376 --> 00:03:21,520
Ms. Kath...

57
00:03:22,397 --> 00:03:24,690
she was the one who helped Ace escape.

58
00:03:25,126 --> 00:03:26,293
She chose to do what's right

59
00:03:26,388 --> 00:03:27,807
instead of following your command.

60
00:03:29,082 --> 00:03:30,193
Liam...

61
00:03:30,832 --> 00:03:33,434
your only ally

62
00:03:35,144 --> 00:03:36,687
turned his back on you.

63
00:03:37,614 --> 00:03:38,840
Liam...

64
00:03:38,865 --> 00:03:41,826
who you killed because
of this crazy obsession!

65
00:03:41,851 --> 00:03:42,810
Enough!

66
00:03:44,838 --> 00:03:46,048
So what?

67
00:03:47,127 --> 00:03:48,503
It's pointless.

68
00:03:49,066 --> 00:03:50,943
Look around you, you're outnumbered.

69
00:05:25,173 --> 00:05:27,133
Is this your grand plan?

70
00:05:27,452 --> 00:05:28,866
It's so pathetic!

71
00:05:29,098 --> 00:05:30,225
I still win!

72
00:05:30,928 --> 00:05:32,311
I am the victor!

73
00:05:34,505 --> 00:05:36,232
After all these years

74
00:05:36,329 --> 00:05:39,248
you came back so I could
kill you and your brother?

75
00:05:39,429 --> 00:05:40,359
Huh?

76
00:05:42,192 --> 00:05:43,131
I came back

77
00:05:43,504 --> 00:05:45,047
to end all of this!

78
00:05:45,747 --> 00:05:46,826
Kill them!

79
00:05:48,231 --> 00:05:49,343
Kill them all!

80
00:06:13,987 --> 00:06:15,080
Surprised?

81
00:06:17,419 --> 00:06:19,087
I am not named Ace

82
00:06:19,358 --> 00:06:20,649
without one.

83
00:06:21,594 --> 00:06:23,179
I don't know your secrets.

84
00:06:25,016 --> 00:06:26,044
Yes, you do.

85
00:06:26,532 --> 00:06:27,533
Promise.

86
00:06:29,851 --> 00:06:30,935
Let's go?

87
00:06:40,937 --> 00:06:42,558
Violet, let’s go.

88
00:08:09,989 --> 00:08:10,989
Zein!

89
00:08:12,371 --> 00:08:13,289
Zein!

90
00:08:15,165 --> 00:08:16,138
Zein!

91
00:08:19,075 --> 00:08:19,907
Matt!

92
00:08:23,236 --> 00:08:24,320
Are you okay?

93
00:08:24,425 --> 00:08:25,104
Zein!

94
00:08:32,975 --> 00:08:34,003
Zein...

95
00:08:44,029 --> 00:08:44,863
Hey!

96
00:08:45,166 --> 00:08:46,918
Madam Violet is escaping!

97
00:08:48,949 --> 00:08:50,065
Stop them!

98
00:08:50,909 --> 00:08:51,760
Hurry!

99
00:08:51,785 --> 00:08:52,995
Go after them!

100
00:08:54,079 --> 00:08:55,124
Are you okay, Nicky?

101
00:08:55,831 --> 00:08:57,403
Isn’t this obvious enough for you?

102
00:09:11,837 --> 00:09:13,136
Stop staring!

103
00:09:13,682 --> 00:09:14,933
Or I'll pull the trigger.

104
00:09:15,851 --> 00:09:17,068
I'm not joking!

105
00:09:18,870 --> 00:09:20,329
What's your problem?

106
00:09:21,325 --> 00:09:22,433
I'm dying...

107
00:09:24,129 --> 00:09:25,003
Huh?

108
00:09:27,237 --> 00:09:28,489
What are you talking about?

109
00:09:30,761 --> 00:09:31,748
It’s the poison...

110
00:09:32,606 --> 00:09:34,191
It’s spreading in my bloodstream.

111
00:09:37,736 --> 00:09:38,863
Then die.

112
00:10:05,067 --> 00:10:06,402
Nazzer!

113
00:10:07,152 --> 00:10:08,153
Nazzer!

114
00:10:08,779 --> 00:10:10,181
Nazzer!

115
00:10:12,991 --> 00:10:14,247
Nazzer!

116
00:10:20,155 --> 00:10:21,781
Nazzer!

117
00:10:24,586 --> 00:10:26,046
You bastard, wake up!

118
00:10:26,071 --> 00:10:26,780
Please...

119
00:10:29,967 --> 00:10:31,582
Wake up!

120
00:10:32,553 --> 00:10:33,536
Please!

121
00:10:34,054 --> 00:10:37,558
Are you going to die now
that we're almost free?

122
00:10:38,317 --> 00:10:39,256
Please!

123
00:10:43,178 --> 00:10:45,206
Please, wake up.

124
00:11:07,004 --> 00:11:08,328
I love you, Nazzer.

125
00:11:12,760 --> 00:11:14,156
I love you too, bitch.

126
00:11:17,806 --> 00:11:19,475
Fuck you, you're still alive!

127
00:11:20,642 --> 00:11:21,706
I've been crying my eyes out

128
00:11:21,731 --> 00:11:22,730
and you're still alive!

129
00:11:24,584 --> 00:11:25,877
I knew you love me.

130
00:11:27,026 --> 00:11:28,194
Fuck you!

131
00:11:28,694 --> 00:11:29,665
Come here.

132
00:11:44,708 --> 00:11:46,013
Madam Violet!

133
00:11:46,392 --> 00:11:47,810
We have you surrounded!

134
00:11:48,395 --> 00:11:49,646
Surrender now!

135
00:11:50,464 --> 00:11:52,549
Game over, bitch!

136
00:11:53,592 --> 00:11:54,515
Get out!

137
00:11:54,741 --> 00:11:55,630
Get out!

138
00:12:04,978 --> 00:12:05,871
Madam Violet

139
00:12:05,896 --> 00:12:07,372
- Sir Francisco
- Let go!

140
00:12:07,397 --> 00:12:08,673
you have the right to remain silent.

141
00:12:08,815 --> 00:12:11,783
Anything you say can and will be used
against you in a court of law.

142
00:12:37,302 --> 00:12:37,734
Zein...

143
00:12:37,801 --> 00:12:38,548
Zein!

144
00:12:38,679 --> 00:12:39,154
Zein!

145
00:12:39,179 --> 00:12:40,021
Matt!

146
00:12:42,266 --> 00:12:43,188
Are you okay?

147
00:12:44,031 --> 00:12:45,160
I’m okay, bro.

148
00:12:47,442 --> 00:12:49,206
I thought we would never see you again.

149
00:12:49,231 --> 00:12:50,672
- We’re safe now.
- I thought so too.

150
00:13:00,033 --> 00:13:01,724
I'm grateful that you're all safe.

151
00:13:03,392 --> 00:13:04,852
Thank you for being safe.

152
00:13:05,102 --> 00:13:06,390
You're not alone anymore.

153
00:13:06,817 --> 00:13:07,836
We're here now.

154
00:13:08,333 --> 00:13:09,585
You'll never be alone again.

155
00:13:18,806 --> 00:13:19,849
Guys...

156
00:13:29,118 --> 00:13:30,328
am I dead?

157
00:13:31,148 --> 00:13:33,219
Why am I seeing a ghost?

158
00:13:33,817 --> 00:13:34,985
No, you’re not dead.

159
00:13:35,429 --> 00:13:36,764
That's Ferry.

160
00:13:37,446 --> 00:13:38,544
He's not dead.

161
00:13:39,281 --> 00:13:40,532
It's...

162
00:13:40,813 --> 00:13:41,814
a long story.

163
00:13:45,203 --> 00:13:46,391
I don't understand.

164
00:13:47,592 --> 00:13:48,802
Why are you together?

165
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:51,418
Why aren't you killing each other?

166
00:13:52,984 --> 00:13:54,819
That’s what you wanted to believe.

167
00:13:55,213 --> 00:13:57,122
Nazzer is the leader of the BBG.

168
00:13:57,962 --> 00:13:59,839
I am the leader of the Devil God Warrior.

169
00:14:00,844 --> 00:14:02,346
And I am the President.

170
00:14:05,474 --> 00:14:06,642
But all of us

171
00:14:07,726 --> 00:14:09,394
we're all allies.

172
00:14:10,645 --> 00:14:12,063
We have one goal.

173
00:14:12,872 --> 00:14:14,541
To bring you down

174
00:14:14,566 --> 00:14:17,194
and to stop all the
killings of the students

175
00:14:17,194 --> 00:14:18,237
here in Hell U.

176
00:14:19,010 --> 00:14:20,136
Cause you...

177
00:14:20,836 --> 00:14:22,171
you've only been thinking of one goal...

178
00:14:22,784 --> 00:14:24,452
acquiring the formula.

179
00:14:27,029 --> 00:14:29,406
So while you're busy
searching for the formula

180
00:14:30,665 --> 00:14:33,130
we've been planning a way to escape.

181
00:14:33,282 --> 00:14:34,616
So Raze Silvenia

182
00:14:35,174 --> 00:14:36,426
is just someone you invented?

183
00:14:37,319 --> 00:14:38,302
Yes

184
00:14:39,007 --> 00:14:40,884
There isn't a Rouge Silvenia either.

185
00:14:41,872 --> 00:14:43,829
I'm Lux's only brother.

186
00:14:44,779 --> 00:14:46,155
The one and only.

187
00:14:49,026 --> 00:14:50,652
Do you think I'm stupid?

188
00:14:51,103 --> 00:14:53,146
I saw Rouge's corpse.

189
00:14:55,232 --> 00:14:56,124
Who was that?

190
00:14:56,149 --> 00:14:57,984
Some sacrifices need to happen

191
00:14:58,979 --> 00:15:00,815
for a bigger event to succeed.

192
00:15:01,023 --> 00:15:02,566
To create chaos,

193
00:15:03,615 --> 00:15:04,788
to prove a point.

194
00:15:06,683 --> 00:15:09,746
He sacrificed his life for this moment.

195
00:15:12,040 --> 00:15:15,711
So you took advantage of his death

196
00:15:16,570 --> 00:15:18,914
to show that the gang war is getting worse?

197
00:15:19,739 --> 00:15:21,532
We didn't let him die in vain.

198
00:15:22,346 --> 00:15:23,349
I must say

199
00:15:24,428 --> 00:15:26,096
I'm impressed.

200
00:15:29,015 --> 00:15:30,851
You're just like me.

201
00:15:31,149 --> 00:15:33,715
We're nothing like you, Violet.

202
00:15:34,892 --> 00:15:37,061
We're doing all of this for freedom.

203
00:15:38,316 --> 00:15:39,219
But you...

204
00:15:40,204 --> 00:15:42,344
you've turned this
university into a prison.

205
00:15:43,414 --> 00:15:44,415
So now...

206
00:15:44,975 --> 00:15:46,515
we'll make sure you rot there.

207
00:15:48,827 --> 00:15:50,270
I'm sorry, my love.

208
00:15:51,387 --> 00:15:52,636
I failed you.

209
00:15:53,874 --> 00:15:55,792
I should have made sure

210
00:15:56,422 --> 00:15:59,099
Lux was dead when I left him.

211
00:16:00,798 --> 00:16:02,360
But you're right, Sir Francisco.

212
00:16:04,955 --> 00:16:06,623
I died that night.

213
00:16:09,440 --> 00:16:10,692
That Lux...

214
00:16:11,930 --> 00:16:13,098
he's gone now.

215
00:16:14,277 --> 00:16:15,529
There’s only Raze now.

216
00:16:30,803 --> 00:16:32,335
Be gentle with him, please.

217
00:16:32,562 --> 00:16:33,813
That's my boyfriend.

218
00:16:35,832 --> 00:16:36,837
Calm down.

219
00:16:37,120 --> 00:16:38,445
If something bad happens to him,

220
00:16:38,752 --> 00:16:39,795
I'll hunt you down.

221
00:16:41,580 --> 00:16:42,915
You’re wounded, bro.

222
00:16:43,256 --> 00:16:44,424
What happened to you?

223
00:16:45,252 --> 00:16:46,108
Be careful.

224
00:16:46,134 --> 00:16:46,987
Zein...

225
00:16:47,670 --> 00:16:48,712
this is Lux.

226
00:16:49,300 --> 00:16:50,201
Lux...

227
00:16:50,847 --> 00:16:51,848
this is Zein.

228
00:16:52,641 --> 00:16:53,950
So you're...

229
00:16:53,975 --> 00:16:54,809
Raze.

230
00:17:03,207 --> 00:17:04,249
So...

231
00:17:04,528 --> 00:17:06,404
care to explain what really happened?

232
00:17:08,073 --> 00:17:09,282
The gangs...

233
00:17:10,909 --> 00:17:13,119
did you really orchestrate all that?

234
00:17:16,832 --> 00:17:19,167
In the beginning, revenge
was my only intention.

235
00:17:20,047 --> 00:17:21,132
But Ace

236
00:17:22,379 --> 00:17:23,974
he set me straight.

237
00:17:25,695 --> 00:17:27,488
Revenge shouldn't be our priority.

238
00:17:28,602 --> 00:17:29,714
The prioriy is to

239
00:17:29,928 --> 00:17:31,325
set the students free

240
00:17:32,274 --> 00:17:33,859
and stop this hell.

241
00:17:34,808 --> 00:17:36,852
And while Violet was
preoccupied with the formula

242
00:17:37,185 --> 00:17:38,289
we took her distraction

243
00:17:38,812 --> 00:17:39,982
as a chance to make a move.

244
00:17:40,647 --> 00:17:43,066
One by one, we started
setting the students free.

245
00:17:45,878 --> 00:17:47,546
The ones released
coordinated with the police

246
00:17:47,571 --> 00:17:48,905
to locate Hell U.

247
00:17:50,230 --> 00:17:51,731
So they can make a warrant.

248
00:17:57,264 --> 00:17:58,474
What about Dark Hell Jail?

249
00:17:59,749 --> 00:18:00,620
Ferry?

250
00:18:01,767 --> 00:18:03,102
Is he an informant?

251
00:18:05,881 --> 00:18:07,132
Jerome helped us

252
00:18:07,620 --> 00:18:10,519
to smuggle students out of here
when he became part of the DGW.

253
00:18:15,958 --> 00:18:18,086
You even involved my friend?

254
00:18:19,363 --> 00:18:20,948
We didn't force them.

255
00:18:21,980 --> 00:18:23,398
They wanted to help us.

256
00:18:33,366 --> 00:18:35,827
Dave was the first to
figure out our operations.

257
00:18:36,578 --> 00:18:38,371
He found out that we’re
helping students escape.

258
00:18:38,496 --> 00:18:39,873
through the Dark Hell Jail.

259
00:18:41,082 --> 00:18:44,158
That's the secret path
to get out of Hell University.

260
00:18:57,390 --> 00:18:59,537
Then he informed Jerome and Matt.

261
00:18:59,562 --> 00:19:00,521
I want to join

262
00:19:00,852 --> 00:19:01,761
your gang.

263
00:19:03,772 --> 00:19:05,523
That's why they joined BGG.

264
00:19:07,307 --> 00:19:08,558
and DGW.

265
00:19:09,611 --> 00:19:11,029
Take care of them.

266
00:19:13,985 --> 00:19:15,737
There's only one path. Just stay on it.

267
00:19:31,885 --> 00:19:32,813
Fuck.

268
00:19:33,969 --> 00:19:36,221
So while I was doing shit on my own...

269
00:19:36,931 --> 00:19:38,432
You were doing the right thing.

270
00:19:39,140 --> 00:19:41,851
We just wanted to end Hell U
without putting your friends in danger.

271
00:19:42,602 --> 00:19:43,728
You shook the admin.

272
00:19:45,021 --> 00:19:47,315
You inspired the students
to stand up against Violet.

273
00:19:48,400 --> 00:19:49,272
But...

274
00:19:49,943 --> 00:19:52,407
we'd never expected you'd
play a bigger part here.

275
00:19:54,219 --> 00:19:57,680
And we also never expected for you to have
the special blood to complete the serum.

276
00:19:58,732 --> 00:20:00,984
It wasn't part of the plan
for you to be in mortal danger.

277
00:20:02,205 --> 00:20:03,790
That was a curveball in that plan.

278
00:20:05,583 --> 00:20:06,554
Curveball?

279
00:20:06,960 --> 00:20:07,814
How?

280
00:20:08,659 --> 00:20:10,452
Because it wasn't part of my plan

281
00:20:12,757 --> 00:20:14,050
to fall in love with you.

282
00:20:22,559 --> 00:20:24,060
And this brother of mine

283
00:20:24,794 --> 00:20:27,370
almost died trying to save you, Zein.

284
00:20:29,315 --> 00:20:30,458
Is it my fault

285
00:20:30,483 --> 00:20:31,771
that your brother is an idiot?

286
00:20:33,629 --> 00:20:34,532
Er...

287
00:20:35,057 --> 00:20:35,957
Wow.

288
00:20:36,524 --> 00:20:37,544
You're welcome.

289
00:20:39,361 --> 00:20:40,404
By the way

290
00:20:42,845 --> 00:20:43,791
Shit!

